# Commit & Branch Conventions

## Conventional Commits

```
<type>(<scope>): <imperative description>

[optional body]

[optional footer]
```

### Types

| Type | Quando |
|---|---|
| `feat` | Funcionalidade nova |
| `fix` | Correção de bug |
| `refactor` | Refatoração sem mudar comportamento |
| `chore` | Tooling, deps, configs |
| `docs` | Documentação |
| `test` | Adicionar/ajustar testes |
| `perf` | Performance |
| `security` | Correção/melhoria de segurança |
| `migration` | Mudança de schema/DB |

### Scopes principais

`backend`, `frontend`, `crm`, `botify`, `saa`, `insight-ai`, `auth`, `monorepo`, `prisma`, `docs`.

### Exemplos

```
feat(insight-ai): add MVP module for conversation analytics
fix(auth): reject expired refresh tokens
migration(prisma): add tenantId to all operational tables
security(webhooks): verify whatsapp signature before processing
chore(monorepo): bump pnpm to 9.12
```

## Branches

```
feature/<scope>-<short-name>      # feature/insight-ai-mvp
fix/<scope>-<short-name>          # fix/tenant-isolation-leads
security/<scope>-<short-name>     # security/webhook-signature-validation
chore/<short-name>                # chore/bump-deps
```

Sem espaços, sem CamelCase, kebab-case.

## PR checklist (no description)

```markdown
## Summary
- (1-3 bullets, what changed)

## Type
- [ ] feat
- [ ] fix
- [ ] refactor
- [ ] migration
- [ ] security

## Affected modules
- backend/insight-ai
- frontend/dashboard

## Risk review
- [ ] Tenant isolation preserved (queries scoped by tenantId)
- [ ] Auth/permissions added or unchanged
- [ ] No new secrets/PII exposure
- [ ] Migration tested locally
- [ ] Tests added/updated
- [ ] Docs updated

## Test plan
- (passo a passo de como testar)
```

## NÃO

- ❌ Commits "wip", "fix stuff", "asdf"
- ❌ Commits gigantes (>500 linhas alterando 10 escopos)
- ❌ `git push --force` em `main`/`develop`
- ❌ Skipar pre-commit hook com `--no-verify`
